<p>Mandalas, a meadow in the noosphere, and an Eldritch being who is humanity's cleanup sponge.</p>
<p><em>I moved and trimmed your thread summary, since it was taking up extra space in the main forum screen. Try to keep thread descriptions (the text in the little box under the thread title) and titles short so you don't crowd out other authors in the forum listing. ~Zyn</em><br />
