<p>Concerns:</p>
<ul>
<li>Coherence</li>
<li>Consistency</li>
<li>Dialogue</li>
<li>Clinical tone</li>
<li>Pacing</li>
<li>Plot</li>
<li>Understandability (so, coherence, I guess)</li>
