			<div class="content" id="post-content-4857724">
									

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;line&nbsp;by&nbsp;line</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;line&nbsp;by&nbsp;line</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Special Containment Procedures: SCP-XXXX and its related anomalies are undetectable by individuals without sufficient anti-memetics training, therefore standard visual containment is not required.</p>
<p>You could throw in a few more details here. Maybe psychedelics or some other drug or circumstance allows people to see it.</p>
<p>Description: SCP-XXXX is a red mandala that has presence on a global scale and manifests in any population center, regardless of population size.</p>
<p>I think this one might be phrased better as “SCP-XXXX Is an anomalous mandala that has been observed appearing in multiple population centers.” or something like that</p>
<p>SCP-XXXX-1 is largely comprised of a meadow with an abundance of grass and blooming flowers with warm colors. It frequently changes in topography and incorporates structures and large-scale events of mass hysteria from reality.</p>
<p>Are these reenactments of the events? Is this a time jumping thing?</p>
<p>SCP-XXXX-2 is an entity of varying form that is located in SCP-XXXX-1. MTF Omicron Rho (&quot;The Dream Team&quot;) discovered SCP-XXXX-2 in their deployment into SCP-XXXX-1. See addenda.</p>
<p>An “Entity of Varying form” is a very loose description. Do they know the entity is the same entity as before because it’s sapient and speaks to them or something?</p>
<p>Discovery: SCP-XXXX's first documented influence was in the South Florida Baptist Church located on Belvedere Road. When the congregation underwent substantial changes in behavior while in prayer.</p>
<p>You might want to include a town name here. Also, perhaps “While in prayer” could be replaced with “while the parishioners were praying”</p>
<p>Several individuals rose from their benches and sprinted down the middle aisle, screaming in the manner of chimpanzees. Another significant portion of the congregation bit the wooden pews in an attempt to consume portion of the marble that were comprised of.</p>
<p>Did the foundation discover this due to installed CCTV cameras? Witness reports?</p>
<p>After three more similar incidents, the Foundation dispatched field agents to survey the surroundings.</p>
<p>Honestly I could see them doing an investigation after this happened once.</p>
<p>their comms devices drenched</p>
<p>“their comms devices were discovered drenched”</p>
<p>. Experimental Foundation technology was used to record low quality and incomplete video footage of the events that transpired.</p>
<p>This could use a rephrasing, it sounds like the foundation was trying to collect low quality and incomplete video footage the way it’s phrased now</p>
<p>All nun in the church: Meow!</p>
<p>“Nuns”</p>
<p>Opening is not geographically part of any rock formation</p>
<p>“The opening resembles no known rock formation”</p>
<p>“Movement appears in the distance”</p>
<p>“Movement is detected”</p>
<p>&lt;The individuals in the Foundation fatigues have no hands or feets; their legs and arms end in [REDACTED] and they levitate and float towards Myantharun at high speeds.&gt;</p>
<p>Redactions are to be used quite sparingly. Is this one absolutely necessary?</p>
<p>The tip of the creature reaches for a Mandala hovering above in mid-air, burrows into it and leaves.</p>
<p>“And vanishes” or “And disappears” might be better.</p>
<p>Video feed abruptly changes to a long brick road with tanks and nazis marching towards Hero on both sides.</p>
<p>You might consider replacing Nazis with “Nazi stormtroopers” or something more specific like that.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>CONSIDERATIONS:</p>
<p>I’ll admit… I’m not sure what’s going on here. I understand that there’s a group a dreams associated with this snake vomiting guy that can transfer the hallucinations over to reality, but other than that I’m a bit lost as to what’s going on. A lot of the imagery in the skip is nice and surreal though and I think this could be fun if we had a bit more of an idea as to what was happening.</p>

							</div>

								
					
